    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You can use our official image which (as far as I know) retains all the tags: https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/pkgs/container/foundry\r\n\r\nAs for replicating this behavior with `foundryup`, this is not something we want to do yet - we're aiming to stabilize, but until then we will retain 3 nightlies only, so I am going to close this as a \"won't fix\". We are also aiming to replace the current `foundryup` (written in Bash) with a native version with new features, so we are not actively adding new ones to the existing version. Let me know if I misunderstood something!",
